summary: This `moviepage4.html` file contributes a new movie page to the system. It includes a layout for displaying movie information, such as the movie title ("La La Land"), poster image, trailer video, summary, and a rating system using star icons. Users can rate the movie by clicking on the stars and submitting their rating. The file also includes a menu for navigation to other pages in the system and a home button for easy access. Additionally, it links to external CSS and JavaScript files for styling and functionality.
